---
# DEPRECATED — kept only as a fallback example.
#
# As of task #45 (cert-manager + internal CA), longhorn.<local_domain> is
# defined in k8s/ingress/local-ingress.yml.j2 and rendered by
# 03-post-install.yml. Re-running `make all` (or `make post-install`)
# applies the templated version with TLS via the homielab-internal issuer.
#
# Do NOT apply this file alongside the templated one — they share the
# Ingress name `longhorn-local`, so whichever is applied last wins.
# If you have an old gitignored ingress.local.yml in this directory,
# delete it after rolling out the new templated ingress:
#   kubectl -n longhorn-system delete ingress longhorn-ingress 2>/dev/null  # legacy name, if present
#   rm k8s/longhorn/ingress.local.yml
